data.description: Horse property in Kempner! 4 bedroom 2.5 bath 2 car garage! 2 stall barn with tack room. This awesome Lampasas county property in sought after Chica Ranch is just what you have been looking for! The 4 bedrooms are nice size with HUGE closets. New carpet in the master bedroom. New wood laminate floors in the living and formal dining. The gates open up to a lovely drive to your new home. The home includes a beautiful brick fireplace with builtins. Surround sound in the living room. Tiled entry, wet areas and kitchen. Jetted tub, separate shower, his and her sinks (you never have to share again!) in the master bath. Storage shed. Fenced and cross fenced and so much more! You must see this home the pictures are great but nothing beats seeing it in person!
